{"tid":1607102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日仲差一個職業","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:38:24.000Z","uid":6152,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7b86d0a98252a7dcb406011b628e0c513dcb0d","tid":1607102,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"戰地記者<br />\n聽日7區<br />\n記者一定唔撚夠<br />\n而且到時封哂交通 記者好難周圍走<br />\n所以聽日唔係前線full gear 嘅人<br />\n可以開個新fb account <br />\n到時有data就好似立場咁做直播<br />\n無data 就錄影 <br />\n任何落鳩中共面畫面 即時放TG 比唔敢出黎嘅人做文宣<br />\n因為你地錄嘅影隨時會成為歷史一部分<br />\n更可以有機會救到手足<br />\n所以我呼籲多啲人做戰地記者<br />\n(離遠錄又好) (係高嘅地方錄都好）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更何況<br />\n班狗叫人唔好錄影<br />\n敵人擁護的 你懂的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該手足幫手推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n祝各位手足聽日武運昌隆<br />\n願不久將來 煲底相見"},{"pid":"b108b49c398de13d50dc2b934f9b94e42f6d0da2","tid":1607102,"uid":42392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"［戰術討論］聽日6區方向究竟係點［緊急］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"12cf16aa31a1f36d270d8ef3d7a4606f974d734d","tid":1607102,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3143b47b52cd263ace6f52af15580827580aaa90","tid":1607102,"uid":152966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"唉屌想like但手殘<br />\n推"},{"pid":"665490bcb9ba0a6669be690a6ab19ae0ccba89fa","tid":1607102,"uid":25133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n呢個職業重要<br />\n特別係留意到每次如果真係唔好彩<br />\n班狗拉到人 你埋去影好多時都剩係趕你<br />\n唔會